{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2183137, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "里面都是学不会物理的伞兵，不用理", "timestamp": 1627789023, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183222, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "肯定会有阻力啊 虽然不一定能阻止文字到车尾", "timestamp": 1627790181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183255, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我寻思不是有相对移动的趋势就有阻力了嘛。。。", "timestamp": 1627790658, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183256, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "静摩擦不行吗", "timestamp": 1627790680, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183287, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "用等效原理容易理解，加速时相当于高铁末尾有个引力源，蚊子如果不扇翅膀不借桌面摩擦力，自然会往后掉的", "timestamp": 1627791376, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183291, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183222, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 我没有否认有阻力啊，我是说蚊子还是会被甩到车尾，如果蚊子不施加向前飞的力的话。但有人觉得高铁加速的时候，蚊子与高铁是相对静止的", "timestamp": 1627791443, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183294, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183287, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 是这样的", "timestamp": 1627791468, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183297, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183255, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 空气阻力不存在静摩擦这个概念", "timestamp": 1627791478, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183364, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183297, "tag": null, "text": "这些人没体会过公交车急刹车吗。。。。", "timestamp": 1627792466, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183374, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : dz是妹子吧，哈哈哈，可可爱爱吖", "timestamp": 1627792627, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183384, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183364, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 以及推背感", "timestamp": 1627792714, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183405, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "高铁在加速的时候，车后端的空气受到压缩，压强增大，然后产生了从后向前的压强梯度，蚊子就被往前压了，感觉这样说就行", "timestamp": 1627792969, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183485, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183405, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 你的意思其实是惯性力引起的等效空气浮力，但是这个浮力大小不足以抵消惯性力", "timestamp": 1627794081, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183512, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183485, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 达到稳态之后应该能抵消？蚊子在车里的位置应该会靠后一些，但是似乎到不了车尾", "timestamp": 1627794347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183526, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183485, "tag": null, "text": "Re Isabella: 啊不是浮力，是身前和身后的空气密度差带来的压强梯度", "timestamp": 1627794442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183552, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183526, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: BV1wM4y1T7WS，按照这个视频讲的，空气浮力不足以抵消惯性力。所以蚊子是先向后加速，然后匀速飞，所以只要高铁一直加速(或者说蚊子一开始就距离车尾很近)，蚊子就会到车尾", "timestamp": 1627794711, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183565, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183512, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 只要蚊子不主动往前飞，达到稳态就是匀速飞了，而不会相对车厢静止。只有蚊子施加向前的力，才可能喝车厢相对静止", "timestamp": 1627794819, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183588, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183565, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那其实是这样的，就是蚊子的密度和空气的密度对比，比如在车顶吊一个铅球，在开车的时候剪断绳子，铅球还是会碰到车尾。\n\n蚊子密度够小的话，张开翅膀就被压强梯度往前推了", "timestamp": 1627795097, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183697, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "网络伞兵太多了，和一群小学生杠什么啊", "timestamp": 1627796108, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183838, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183512, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 这浮力可以忽略不计吧，要不然蚊子应该可以直接飘在空中", "timestamp": 1627797604, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183849, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183588, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 翅膀很薄，两边没什么压差", "timestamp": 1627797697, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2183877, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 422998, "reply_to": 2183588, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 惯性力相比蚊子翅膀飞的时候受的力基本是忽略不计，稍微扇两下就不用动了，靠阻力需要的速度也很小。蚊子在空中的时候翅膀肯定是一直在动的。这种问题好无聊", "timestamp": 1627797925, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 9, "pid": 422998, "reply": 22, "tag": null, "text": "高铁上的蚊子会不会因为高铁的加速被甩到车尾?就这个问题，dz在别人视频下面留言说，如果蚊子不往前飞的话，就会被甩到车尾。就这么一句话一直被杠，说什么空气阻力会让蚊子向前飞，不会甩到车尾。我在想你要有空气阻力，那不就得蚊子相对车厢向后移动吗？自己打自己脸，还不自知。。。气死我了，一直被人回复，看到小红点又得进去看一下", "timestamp": 1627788953, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627797926, "url": "", "vote": {}}}